{"tid":2034502,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中國豬肉進口四月暴增170% 史上最多 想問下葉劉有咩睇法","createTime":"2020-05-25T09:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T09:41:04.000Z","uid":99695,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"432b5c3771749cd5313a4d09e486f554373953e3","tid":2034502,"uid":99695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:22:05.000Z","msg":"葉劉: 「點獨立呀？無講食水，你豬肉都搞唔掂啦。」香港冇大陸豬死左啦。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073737\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073737&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3o429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=6f76f61c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073737&h=1889416b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073737</a><br />\n<br />\nBEIJING (Reuters) - China, the world&rsquo;s top pork consumer, imported a record 400,000 tonnes in April, up nearly 170% from a year earlier, customs data showed, as buyers took advantage of low prices to stock up on meat.<br />\n<br />\nFILE PHOTO: Pork for sale is seen at Sanyuanli market in Beijing, China May 23, 2019. REUTERS/Jason Lee<br />\nChina imported 1.35 million tonnes of pork in the first four months of this year, surging 170.4% from the same period a year ago, after a plunge in domestic production kept prices much higher than other markets.<br />\n<br />\nThe deadly African swine fever disease has reduced China&rsquo;s pig herd by at least 40%, slashing pork output and sending prices of the country&rsquo;s favorite meat to record highs.<br />\n<br />\nChina has been buying from overseas markets, including the United States, where pork prices are among the cheapest in the world, and initially fell as infections with COVID-19 began spreading in the country, hitting demand.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-economy-trade-pork/chinas-pork-imports-in-april-jump-170-to-record-high-idUSKBN231093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-china-economy-trade-pork%2Fchinas-pork-imports-in-april-jump-170-to-record-high-idUSKBN231093&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3o429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=5c2366bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-china-economy-trade-pork%2Fchinas-pork-imports-in-april-jump-170-to-record-high-idUSKBN231093&h=8f568ea4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-economy-trade-pork/chinas-pork-imports-in-april-jump-170-to-record-high-idUSKBN231093</a>"},{"pid":"2cbae3c78eb5be6710743ae7aae7771215772a0f","tid":2034502,"uid":99695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:22:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"146b9acc14fde4d13872f4ed5d5ca63ad2e20628","tid":2034502,"uid":355943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:23:07.000Z","msg":"孽瘤: 我盲咗"},{"pid":"7d8d97e1ae06754369951e65b2524ee74dea9640","tid":2034502,"uid":99695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:25:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca13f50c2ce9ed90136ab8538a9767c5133ac53c","tid":2034502,"uid":99695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:25:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1c8f55b01b6f2c3a35988fea9ca7d4ee2877e80","tid":2034502,"uid":99695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:25:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b9b831d6b0b856a17300694a3e31422874b35a2","tid":2034502,"uid":99695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:25:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30cd3b889a509165c0c3e0a3be1a49ac49fc2b14","tid":2034502,"uid":235015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:31:21.000Z","msg":"食美國既豬<br />\n飲澳洲既奶水<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\